We never agreed to this!

995
01:27:08,580 --> 01:27:12,670
In the garden, there was a serpent
who tempted Eve.

996
01:27:13,330 --> 01:27:16,350
Leading to man's banishment from paradise.

997
01:27:18,100 --> 01:27:21,870
That serpent has stood between us and 
paradise ever since.

998
01:27:22,260 --> 01:27:24,260
What's this about, Carpathia?

999
01:27:24,710 --> 01:27:26,720
It's about you 2.

1000
01:27:27,430 --> 01:27:32,350
Serpents in my garden. Using unity and
prosperity for your own gain.

1001
01:27:34,730 --> 01:27:37,150
Nikolai, you know, that's preposterous.

1002
01:27:37,370 --> 01:27:39,400
Do not lie to me!

1003
01:27:42,650 --> 01:27:46,180
So small!..so easily manipulated!

1004
01:27:47,090 --> 01:27:50,210
Tell me Jonathan, who is the 
puppet here?

1005
01:27:51,830 --> 01:27:53,940
Look where I am, and look
where you are.

1006
01:27:54,240 --> 01:27:58,610
Do you have any idea, do you know
who you're dealing with?

1007
01:27:59,800 --> 01:28:01,800
Do you?

1008
01:28:03,300 --> 01:28:06,160
I welcome all of you to join this great team.

1009
01:28:07,810 --> 01:28:09,810
Do you accept my invitation?

1010
01:28:12,070 --> 01:28:15,100
We made you, Nikolai. You're
our creation!

1011
01:28:16,740 --> 01:28:18,750
I see!

1012
01:28:22,620 --> 01:28:25,010
Donald M. Otterness?

1013
01:28:25,600 --> 01:28:27,240
Yes sir, that's me.

1014
01:28:27,240 --> 01:28:29,240
Of New York, New Jersey?

1015
01:28:29,240 --> 01:28:30,920
Why, yes sir.

1016
01:28:30,920 --> 01:28:32,920
May I call you Don?

1017
01:28:34,090 --> 01:28:36,430
Don, give me your sidearm.

1018
01:28:42,340 --> 01:28:45,300
So begins an object lesson in
leadership.

1019
01:28:45,530 --> 01:28:47,540
Nikolai.

1020
01:28:47,690 --> 01:28:49,670
Have you lost your mind?
What are you doing?

1021
01:28:51,800 --> 01:28:53,880
- Nikolai!
- Sit down, Chaim.

1022
01:29:02,940 --> 01:29:07,020
Look, we all want the same thing, right?

1023
01:29:07,700 --> 01:29:09,710
I'm sure you're right.

1024
01:29:10,600 --> 01:29:13,530
Ms. Durham, could you please step back?

1025
01:29:13,890 --> 01:29:15,900
I wouldn't want that suit to be soiled.

1026
01:29:20,480 --> 01:29:22,490
On your knees, Johnathan!

1027
01:29:23,400 --> 01:29:26,420
No! No, I will do no such thing!

1028
01:29:34,990 --> 01:29:37,080
- Someone has to stop this!
- Buck!

1029
01:29:38,920 --> 01:29:40,910
We're all on the same team.

1030
01:29:41,490 --> 01:29:43,490
Are we not?

1031
01:29:50,520 --> 01:29:53,690
People will know that I fear no one.

1032
01:29:53,990 --> 01:29:58,490
That I fear nothing! That I will succeed
at anythingI set my mind to!

1033
01:29:58,810 --> 01:30:02,040
Without the slightest hesitation or opposition.

1034
01:30:03,120 --> 01:30:06,300
From this day forth, no one can
stand against me!

1035
01:30:06,980 --> 01:30:10,200
That's the kind of power you lusted
for, Jonathan!

1036
01:30:11,550 --> 01:30:15,080
Don't worry. 
This will be completely painless.

1037
01:30:16,070 --> 01:30:18,850
After all, I am not a monster.

1038
01:30:20,710 --> 01:30:22,710
No, Nikolai, please!

1039
01:30:32,150 --> 01:30:36,590
I was so shocked when I saw Mr. Stonagal 
thrust a guard and take his gun

1040
01:30:37,120 --> 01:30:42,210
and murder his dear friend Mr. Cothran
in cold blood.

1041
01:30:42,540 --> 01:30:45,460
Then, to watch him turn the gun 
on himself,

1042
01:30:46,330 --> 01:30:48,350
it seemed inconceivable.

1043
01:30:49,720 --> 01:30:51,730
But Jonathan was a troubled man.

1044
01:30:52,360 --> 01:30:54,700
Played by guilt, fear.

1045
01:30:55,710 --> 01:31:00,810
And when he heard Mr. Williams was about to expose
him, he knew that it was over.

1046
01:31:01,240 --> 01:31:04,770
He knew that his hideous and evil plan
would come out,

1047
01:31:05,200 --> 01:31:11,900
and that his life, legacy, everything he worked
so long and hard for, would be ruined.

1048
01:31:15,010 --> 01:31:19,930
I know you wanted to do that,
for Dirk and Alan.

1049
01:31:22,470 --> 01:31:26,040
But I couldn't have my new media liaison
with blood on his hands.

1050
01:31:28,260 --> 01:31:30,290
I have big plans for you, Buck.

1051
01:31:30,840 --> 01:31:35,680
That story I sent to the GNN about Stonagal
and Cothran should be airing now any moment.

1052
01:31:36,620 --> 01:31:39,490
The whole world will feel sympathy and
love for me,

1053
01:31:39,490 --> 01:31:41,800
and they will follow me
wherever I lead them.

1054
01:31:43,140 --> 01:31:45,150
Because of you.

1055
01:31:45,800 --> 01:31:47,810
So thank you, Buck.

1056
01:31:49,360 --> 01:31:51,390
Thank you.

1057
01:31:54,540 --> 01:31:56,570
I think we are all in agreement.

1058
01:31:59,180 --> 01:32:03,280
Two lives taken in tragedy.

1059
01:32:06,150 --> 01:32:08,160
All because of greed.

1060
01:32:10,230 --> 01:32:12,240
How terribly sad!

1061
01:32:15,060 --> 01:32:18,100
- Terribly sad!
- Terribly sad!

1062
01:32:18,150 --> 01:32:21,450
- Terribly sad!
- Terribly sad!

1063
01:32:21,800 --> 01:32:23,800
- Terribly sad!

1064
01:32:31,850 --> 01:32:33,850
It's time to change history!

1065
01:32:40,440 --> 01:32:43,360
- Nobody move!
- Johnathan! Johnathan!

1066
01:32:43,720 --> 01:32:45,720
Oh, now!

1067
01:32:46,990 --> 01:32:48,990
Why?

1068
01:32:50,040 --> 01:32:52,420
Ladies and gentlemen! Get back, please!

1069
01:32:53,160 --> 01:32:56,020
Both dead. Let's get the delegates out
of here right now. 

1070
01:32:56,200 --> 01:32:59,900
Ladies and gentlemen, please, clear this room
now! This way, please!

1071
01:32:59,900 --> 01:33:03,150
- Are you OK?
- Seal all doors. Lock this place down now!

1072
01:33:03,530 --> 01:33:05,540
Get back right now!

1073
01:33:11,410 --> 01:33:13,420
Chaim! Chaim!

1074
01:33:15,420 --> 01:33:17,400
What did you see?

1075
01:33:18,360 --> 01:33:22,300
I saw Mr. Stonagal grab the gun from
 the guard's belt,

1076
01:33:22,830 --> 01:33:28,060
shoot Mr. Cothran. And then he shouted something
about wanting forgiveness.

1077
01:33:28,900 --> 01:33:31,380
Then turned the gun on himself.
So awful!

1078
01:33:32,270 --> 01:33:34,250
You saw it!

1079
01:33:35,030 --> 01:33:37,040
Chaim! Nikolai!

1080
01:33:38,380 --> 01:33:41,300
- What about Nikolai?
- Oh, the poor man..

1081
01:33:42,080 --> 01:33:44,780
He was so deceived, he was so
heart-broken.

1082
01:33:45,960 --> 01:33:48,630
Imagine, his own best friends!

1083
01:33:58,980 --> 01:34:01,010
Buck! Buck, are you OK?

1084
01:34:01,590 --> 01:34:04,200
- Hattie, this is unbelievable!
- I know, it's horrible!

1085
01:34:04,200 --> 01:34:06,200
So tragic.

1086
01:34:06,290 --> 01:34:08,310
When Stonagal grabbed that gun..

1087
01:34:10,520 --> 01:34:12,530
Hattie!

1088
01:34:13,540 --> 01:34:15,870
- Hattie, you are in such..
- I know..

1089
01:34:17,240 --> 01:34:19,250
Privileged position.

1090
01:34:19,730 --> 01:34:21,730
I intend to do whatever I can to 
help Nikolai.

1091
01:34:23,020 --> 01:34:25,050
He's a great man.

1092
01:34:33,400 --> 01:34:35,400
I have to go.

1093
01:34:47,250 --> 01:34:52,810
What is evident is the courage of Nikolai Carpathia
in exposing this evil plan..

1094
01:34:53,240 --> 01:34:58,150
And yet the head of UN continues to show no
regard for his own personal safety,

1095
01:34:58,770 --> 01:35:03,530
and yet has vowed to press forward with
his peace initiatives and disarmaments.

1096
01:35:03,890 --> 01:35:09,490
In a world sadly lacking of leadership, Carpathia
stands out as a beacon of hope for the lost.

1097
01:35:12,420 --> 01:35:14,440
Everything the Bible predicted is
happening.

1098
01:35:15,860 --> 01:35:20,480
If this is true, and the Antichrist is coming to
power, then this is just the beginning.

1099
01:35:21,650 --> 01:35:25,150
The next 7 years are going to be the worst
that mankind has ever seen.

1100
01:35:27,030 --> 01:35:29,030
Our only hope is to join together..

1101
01:35:29,580 --> 01:35:31,590
.. and trust God.

1102
01:35:33,180 --> 01:35:35,190
